    <p class="section-number">Related sub-services and brands</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Other patio heater service.</h2>
    <ul class="bullet-list">
      <li><a href="/outdoor/patio-heater-repair/">Patio heater repair (parent pillar)</a></li>
      <li><a href="/outdoor/patio-heater-repair/not-igniting/">Not igniting</a></li>
      <li><a href="/outdoor/patio-heater-repair/flame-out/">Flame out (lights then dies)</a></li>
      <li><a href="/outdoor/patio-heater-repair/restaurant-patio/">Restaurant patio service</a></li>
      <li><a href="/outdoor/patio-heater-repair/brands/infratech/">Infratech</a> · <a href="/outdoor/patio-heater-repair/brands/solaira/">Solaira</a> · <a href="/outdoor/patio-heater-repair/brands/aei/">AEI</a></li>
      <li><a href="/outdoor/patio-heater-repair/brands/bromic/">Bromic</a> · <a href="/outdoor/patio-heater-repair/brands/sunpak/">Sunpak</a> · <a href="/outdoor/patio-heater-repair/brands/schwank/">Schwank</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bottom-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Wall-Mounted Patio Heater Repair? Call Today.</h2>
